text:
When we took this offer, it felt like it was in the distant future 
but looking back on it, the time went by in an instant.

Well when your lazing around,
time tends to fly by like that an all.

Haha...... Even still,
I saw that you were giving your best effort, Mamimi.

......
Well, I guess I gave it a little bit of effort

But, if you've acknowledged my efforts, then it should be
okay to expect a reward, right Producer?

Ugh... Taking that approach, huh...
Well, if your performance goes off without a hitch, I'll think about it... haha

I guess I'll go get this over with so
just watch from right there.
